title: Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015 KPBS Evening Edition KPBS San Diego
text: San Diego County's economy takes a $1B hit from low enrollment in safety net programs. Plus, we talk with filmmaker Paul Espinosa and continue our Balboa Park memories series.
